    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained executive vehicle that exemplifies both engineering excellence and sophisticated design. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure mechanical reliability and structural integrity. The interior remains refined, reflecting a history of responsible ownership and consistent care. Offering a seamless blend of performance and comfort, this vehicle represents a premier acquisition for the professional driver. Detailed service records are available to verify its documented maintenance pedigree.",
      "price": 34850.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
