      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly loved? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and let me tell you, it\u2019s a total gem! It runs like a dream and is in great shape for its next owner. Whether you're commuting or heading out for a weekend getaway, this beauty is ready to go. Come take it for a spin\u2014you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused BMW E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring a 7,900 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous response. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering tactile engagement through every gate. Maintenance is up to date, including a vital VANOS system overhaul and a reinforced rear subframe to address common chassis stress points. The variable M differential lock remains sharp, ensuring excellent traction through the apex. The suspension geometry is well-sorted, retaining its factory-spec damping and communicative feedback. While the aesthetic reflects honest road use, the mechanical vitals and powertrain integrity remain in top form for the spirited driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regular maintenance history. Clean title. Runs well. Minor cosmetic wear only.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2020 BMW 330i xDrive finished in classic Alpine White. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance for a discerning buyer looking for luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel\u2014typical of careful daily use. Inside, the Black SensaTec cabin is pristine; the seats show virtually no bolster wear, and the interior has never been smoked in. All technological features, including the iDrive navigation system, heated steering wheel, and Apple CarPlay, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, this BMW is in excellent health with a full service history performed at authorized centers. We recently completed a 40,000-mile service including a fresh oil change, new engine air filters, and a multi-point inspection. The Pirelli all-season tires have plenty of life left, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, representing a superior balance of performance and value. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and long-term reliability. The exterior retains a commendable finish, while the interior remains refined and well-preserved. This is an ideal acquisition for the discerning driver seeking a high-caliber driving experience at a competitive market valuation.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so you know it's ready for many more miles of adventures! It runs smoothly and is just perfect for anyone looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a 2003 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant with VarioCam Plus. This example is equipped with the desirable G96 6-speed manual transaxle. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including an LN Engineering dual-row ceramic IMS bearing upgrade and a recent Rear Main Seal (RMS) replacement. The suspension retains its factory-engineered kinematics with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. Braking is handled by four-piston monobloc calipers over cross-drilled rotors. While the exterior shows minor cosmetic road patina, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response are sharp. A technically sound driver's car for the purist who prioritizes drivetrain integrity and chassis feedback.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
